data.description: Move-in Ready 4 Bedroom, 2.5 Bath home in Main Street! This home has FRESH Interior paint, NEW Carpet, NEW Stainless Steel Kitchen appliances, and space galore! Relax on the covered front porch or back patio overlooking the fenced rear yard! Foyer entry! Beautiful Dining Room with carpet and crown molding! Spacious Great Room features carpet, a vaulted ceiling, ceiling fan, electric fireplace, and access to the rear yard! The Kitchen has vinyl floors, white cabinets, breakfast bar, pantry, NEW Whirlpool electric range, built-in microwave, dishwasher, and refrigerator! The breakfast room overlooks the rear yard and gets plenty of natural light! The Primary Bedroom is located on the main level and has carpet, vaulted ceiling, ceiling fan and an en-suite bath complete with double vanity, garden tub, separate shower, separate water closet, and spacious walk-in closet! The Laundry Room and a 1/2 bath complete the downstairs! Upstairs features 3 bedroom's all with carpet, ceilings fans, blinds, and double closets! One bedroom also has a walk-in attic! Full hall bath with single vanity and tub/shower combo! Another attic, pull-down stairs, and linen closet are located in the landing area! Double car garage! Conveniently located close to Fort Eisenhower, I-20, shopping, schools, and restaurants! Schedule your private viewing today!
